# Ignore executables and output folders in all chapter folders

# Ignore all executables (no matter the name) in any subfolder
**/*

# But explicitly exclude source files and folders you want to keep:
!**/*.c
!**/*.h
!**/*.txt
!README.md

# Ignore all output folders in any chapter folder (named exactly "output")
**/output/

# Ignore common build files and IDE files
*.o
*.exe
*.out
*.obj
*.so
*.dll
*.class

# VS Code settings
.vscode/
